full_text: Front Entrance - Sweep and mop, clean door mats. Outdoor furniture - Pressure wash. Pool - Clean. Check that water temperature is between 82 - 88°F. Exercise equipment - Wipe all equipment, sides and fronts, vacuum behind, check. Garage - Vacuum / sweep out as needed. Cars - Wash and wax exterior, clean and vacuum inside. DATE: ____________________ SIGNATURE: ____________________ 2/14/2005 37 DOJ-OGR-00015766
